## 🔐 2. ENVIRONMENT.md (Tools & App Configuration)

### Required Development Dependencies
All system modules must match the explicit versions below to avoid deployment compilation errors:
*   `streamlit==1.32.0` — Core reactive interface engine.
*   `anthropic==0.18.0` — Official Claude API software development kit.
*   `pandas==2.2.0` — Handles structured data tables.
*   `plotly==5.19.0` — Controls interactive dashboard data visualizations.

### Secure Key Configuration
To connect the Claude reasoning engine securely, create a file named `.env` in the root folder (never commit this file to public GitHub repositories):
```text
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_secret_claude_api_key_here
```

